---
title: Tunisian Stuffed Peppers with Chickpeas, Apricots, & Feta Cheese
description: Didn’t grow up with stuffed peppers? Here’s a quick 101: hollowed-out bell peppers are filled with a combination of protein, grains, vegetables, and spices. Of course, that doesn’t quite sum up how delicious and, for some, nostalgia-inducing they are. This veggie version happens to be extra special. The filling starts with Tunisian-spiced jasmine rice (think turmeric, cinnamon, and smoked paprika) that’s then bejeweled with dried apricots, crispy chickpeas, and salty feta. Prepare for a flavor explosion.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5df00e32a18dc93a36780014-076546fd.jpg
